column5: went last weekend to huntsville to fish at limberlost lodge, private lakes with cabins a little pricy. but all in all a good weekend. the lake our cabin was on was speckles we caught 21 speckles betwwent he 5 of us then saturday we walk to a rainbow and lake trout lake . we got 7 rainbows all in the 18-22 inch range nice eating i have pic just have to download. lots  of ice there. the only draw back was sleeping on air mattresses on bunk beds . till the next trip see ya
